<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَّمًّا}</span> ... شَدِيدًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جَمًّا}</span> ... مُفْرِطًا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{دُكَّتِ}</span> ... زُلْزِلَتْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَجَاءَ رَبُّكَ}</span> ... جَاءَ رَبُّكَ لِفَصْلِ القَضَاءِ بَيْنَ العِبَادِ مَجِيئًا يَلِيقُ بِجَلَالِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْمَلَكُ}</span> ... المَلَائِكَةُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَفًّا صَفًّا}</span> ... صُفُوفًا كَثِيرَةً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَنَّى لَهُ الذِّكْرَى}</span> ... لَا يَنْفَعُهُ التَّذَكُّرُ؛ فَقَدْ فَاتَ أَوَانُهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
